re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:20:13.000Z","msg":"一開時事台 個撚個話輸輸輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dc7399024fd43528c306650e2e9c90a78aa485","tid":1467472,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾post盛行<br />\n善用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6c802922b3cdd9598752a18c999192899c69fa","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:25:43.000Z","msg":"記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼正確方法 (PR最好睇)<br />\n1. 詢問<br />\n2. 控制，防止逃跑<br />\n3. 搵記者，由記者盤問（811記者問黑警扮示威者咁樣）<br />\n5. 睇證件、影相<br />\n6. 散水，不包圍<br />\n<br />\n721 805 811"},{"pid":"be300549b2a76c03cb3cb2b9a34a969ba69827eb","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78dc7399024fd43528c306650e2e9c90a78aa485","tid":1467472,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾post盛行<br />\n善用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:26:15.000Z","msg":"啱 而家好多狗仔上嚟帶風向"},{"pid":"5859accc7a4b7806205408955312d5b5dd337c93","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78dc7399024fd43528c306650e2e9c90a78aa485","tid":1467472,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:21:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾post盛行<br />\n善用不推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:26:31.000Z","msg":"用呢句推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e289290393b0ea87dd012c0f3fb7e1263b7b6de2","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:54.00