c990c74bd284ebec08","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:21:43.000Z","msg":"好撚多垃圾post呀我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:56:11.000Z","msg":"大家都千其唔好做垃圾幫手推post<br />\n記得要開不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26558dca6f71dc872f4249117af2239b36d47177","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:56:20.000Z","msg":"有用post: 正皮 留言推<br />\n垃圾post: 無視/不推文屌"},{"pid":"ac703560e7a3931525ac67ffdf6da5dab6f095dc","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:00:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YZxV9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YZxV9O.png&h=596294f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b1806b30bcef274dcc745112cf8bd042243a068","tid":1467472,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:02:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8612e33067a54480d3fa03f5b935b5472cf5ac6d","tid":1467472,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:06.000Z","msg":"求下大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n與其諗塞機場對錯，不如諗8.16㩒錢經濟戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467538\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467538</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q50QHQ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ50QHQ0.png&h=48e1bded&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUHr0CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUHr0CF.jpg&h=a576b9bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bae2187674f7c5d701d9aafb4e74d07a03d572b2","tid":1467472,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:04:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔會割蓆，但我地亦都會持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩建議大家投票解決，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所以社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，可貴之處就係識得自省，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要認，認完就要反省，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏<br />\n<br />\n如果出現失誤唔去承認，唔去反省，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。"},{"pid":"dbb989796d6d34eac0d4f536ca772eb3ad8c24f9","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"有用post: 正皮 留言推<br />\n垃圾post: 無視/不推文屌"},{"pid":"d4507b340e9fa2330f8c048765693092f2f184e0","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:07:35.000Z","msg":"路過幫手推下 可能有新手未識用/大家一時太嬲唔撳就屌"},{"pid":"5a85e3b1b43996acbb45a78a9aa26cc4dc006cbe","tid":1467472,"uid":200389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:14:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有用post: 正皮 留言推<br />\n垃圾post: 無視/不推文屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"c147188d70db73f8dc45030077c61b7e8a324127","tid":1467472,"uid":78645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:09.000Z","msg":"不推文回覆"},{"pid":"aba816bcfd5b140cf47424c2d0fb33ce4c13e5f5","tid":1467472,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:15:40.000Z","msg":"捉到共狗又唔想就咁放走，<br />\n用幽默手法嘲諷羞辱就夠，<br />\n貼住「平反六四」罰坐，<br />\n破壞證件、報名參軍之類，<br />\n顯得有文化又收威嚇之用。<br />\n<br />\n懲罰並唔一定要流血，<br />\n有時只需要取其象徵意義。<br />\n檯底點懲治黑警都無所謂，<br />\n但檯面一定要好好睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n【反省與建議】「俘虜」處置提案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468537</a>"},{"pid":"9b8b1b79ebf39bf4e695926107a227fe60ea9837","tid":1467472,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"